 FAST WORK: We were supposed to be without full use of the quake-damaged Santa 
Monica Freeway for many months, but Gov. Pete Wilson said Tuesday it will 
reopen next week, possibly Monday (A1). . . . Unfortunately, however, work on 
the bridges near the Antelope Valley and Golden State freeways won't be fully 
completed until early fall. 
