provide insight into the world of children, sharpen parental skills and build a 
network of parents in the community. 
</P>
<P>
 "The Power of Parents" will be the theme for the conference April 16 from 8 
a.m. to noon at Fullerton High, 201 E. Chapman Ave.It is sponsored by Community 
United for Fullerton Safety, Fullerton High and the Coalition for Children, 
Adolescents and Parents. 
</P>
<P>
