<P>
COMMUNITY COLLEGE ATHLETES OF THE WEEK 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Ted Wilkes 
</P>
<P>
 Saddleback, So. 
</P>
<P>
 Baseball / Outfield 
</P>
<P>
 Saddleback went on a hitting terror last week in the Buckman-Mitchell baseball 
tournament in Visalia, and Wilkes led the way.The Gauchos outscored opponents, 
43-14, in four games. Wilkes, selected the tournament's most valuable player, 
