COLLEGE ROUNDUP; UC IRVINE WINS GOLF TOURNAMENT 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 UC Irvine's Gold team won the Anteater Invitational golf tournament with a 
three-round score of 891 Tuesday at Coto de Caza Country Club. 
</P>
<P>
