Vilbiss of San Diego State won the individual title with a three-round total of 
three-over 219. The teams played 36 holes Monday and 18 Tuesday. 
</P>
<P>
 Drew Sells of UC Irvine was second at 220. He shot 74 Tuesday. In 
nonconference baseball: 
