<TEXT>
<P>
 Antelope Valley College scored five runs in the top of the ninth inning to 
pull even with Rio Hondo and scored three in the 11th to earn a 10-7 Foothill 
Conference victory Tuesday at Rio Hondo. 
</P>
<P>
